'''David Nakabayashi''' works at [[Industrial Light & Magic]] as a Visual Effects Art Director.<ref name="TPM" /> He has used his artistic abilities to help make the [[Star Wars: Essential Guides|Essential Guide]] series.<ref name="Essential">''[[The Essential Guide to Weapons and Technology]]''</ref> In [[2002]], Nakabayashi was promoted to the creative director of the ILM art department.<ref name="Insider 208">{{InsiderCite|208|The Art of Effects}}</ref>

